                    <b> Find the secret key on this site: <a href="https://challenge.thecloudbill.com/" target="_blank">challenge.thecloudbil.com</a> </b><br /><br />

                    Brief about the challenge :<br />
                    In this first contest, You have to find the content of the secret file which is on <a href="https://challenge.thecloudbill.com/" target="_blank">the site </a>. Application is intentionally vulnerable and using that vulnerability you have to find the secret key.<br />
                    <br /><br />
