                    <br /><br />

                    <b>Important:</b> <br />This is not the site for the penetration testings. The actual vulnerable site is <a href="https://challenge.thecloudbill.com/" target="_blank">here</a>. (Will be live on 15th August)<br />

                    <br />
                    <b>Instructions</b>:<br />
                    No SQL Injections or XSS will work<br />
                    Don't use DOS or DDOS attack if found then you will be disqualified<br />
                    Application it self written in python Django framework<br />
