            </div>

        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6">

            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-header">
                    <h3>Know Your Emails</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    Know Your Emails<br />
                    <br />
                    Brief about the challenge :<br />
                    <br />
                    As we all know that WhatsApp has a nice feature that tells us whether the recipient has opened your message or not. (not to mention turn offing blue tick 😉)<br />
                    <br />
                    But how about emails??<br /><br />
                    Is there any way to find out whether the recipient had opened your mail or not.<br />
                    <br />
                    Of course, the solution exists<br /><br />
                    And you have to find it in this challenge<br /><br />

                    You have to create a solution for this real-world problem by using the programming language of your choice.<br />
                    <br />
                    Instructions<br />

                    If you think you have the solution then upload it here.<br />
                    You can include anything here but make sure to zip everything in one file.<br />
                    <br />
                    You can use google's solution, but make sure you try and test it before uploading here<br />

                    <br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br />



